DOC.brief_summary: The aim of this study is to compare of different massage techniques plus conservative aplications in low back pain treatment.
DOC.brief_title: Comparison of Different Massage Techniques Plus Conservative Applications in Low Back Pain
DOC.criteria: Having non specific low back pain without any relevant ongoing pathologies such as disc prolapse, spondylolisthesis, fractures, tumor, osteoporosis, infection Willing to participate Spinal surgery in the past 6 months or having to undergo surgery or invasive examinations during the study; neurological disease; psychiatric disease; serious chronic disease that could interfere with the outcomes (e.g., cardiovascular disease, epilepsy, rheumatoid arthritis), pregnant during the study
